name: Stack Capital Group Inc.
longDescription: Stack Capital Group Inc is a newly formed investment holding company. It is focused on investing in growth to late-stage private issuers with operating businesses, with long-term growth potential, located in, or with customers, suppliers or business primarily conducted in or dependent on, Canada or the United States. Its business objective is to maximize its long-term capital appreciation by seeking to achieve superior risk-adjusted investment performance.
